  <brief_title>Measurements to Assess Severity of Epicardial Stenoses</brief_title>
  <acronym>MASES</acronym>
  <official_title>Simultaneous Measurements Of Pressure Gradient, Blood Flow and Percentage Area Stenosis Of Coronary Epicardial Lesions To Assess Severity Of Epicardial Stenosis And Myocardial Infarction</official_title>
